episodes.title: So, You Were Born Into A Cult? | Parvati Shallow (Survivor)
episodes.description:
On today’s episode, CORINNE FISHER and KRYSTYNA HUTCHINSON welcome reality TV star and author, PARVATI SHALLOW, to the studio. The trio discuss being born into a commune, a marriage that feels like a cult, the manipulative nature of producing reality television, and having all the gay s*x your heart desires post-divorce.

Follow this week's guest: @PShallow
